0w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Alison-Moyet-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Alison-Moyet-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Alison-Moyet-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Alison-Moyet-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>艾莉森·莫耶特 (Alison Moyet) 为 BBC 广播二台翻唱了<a href="/artists/David-Bowie">大卫·鲍伊</a>(David Bowie) 的《Absolute Beginners》。</p><p> 6 月 20 日，这位前<a href="/artists/Yazoo">Yazoo</a>成员作为嘉宾出现在 BBC 广播 2 台的钢琴室，演唱了鲍伊 1986 年同名电影中歌曲的明亮翻唱。她还演唱了即将发行的专辑《Key》中的最新单曲《Such Small Ale》和 1984 年的热门单曲《All Cried Out》。您可以<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/sounds/play/m002035f" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>收听她在 BBC 广播 2 台上的完整音频。</p><p>早在 1985 年，莫耶特就在 Live Aid 音乐会上与鲍伊、<a href="/artists/Peter-Townshend">彼得·汤申德</a>和<a href="/artists/Paul-McCartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>同台翻唱了<a href="/artists/The-Beatles">披头士乐队</a>的《Let It Be》。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="艾莉森·莫耶 - BBC 2 广播电台的绝对初学者（大卫·鲍伊的歌曲）（钢琴室）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0HBjw1zD9sU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Alison Moyet - 这样的小啤酒（Radio 2 钢琴室）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Vpo4KC5fy90?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “Key”将于 10 月 4 日发布，可<a href="https://alisonmoyet.lnk.to/Main" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订/预保存</a>。该密纹唱片庆祝 Moyet 作为独唱艺术家 40 周年，收录了她漫长职业生涯中 16 首单曲和曲目的全新版本。</p><p>在一份声明中（ <a href="https://www.brooklynvegan.com/alison-moyet-yazoo-announces-new-album-key-shares-such-small-ale-and-rework-of-all-cried-out/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>布鲁克林素食主义</em></a>者）谈到这张专辑时，莫耶特分享道：“我想借此机会回顾过去四十年的轨迹，探索那些在其原始形式中从未完全实现或已经实现的歌曲。它们与我的相关性随着时间的推移而改变。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8L9xXYxikE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.11