edelic Orgasm》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kim-gordon-shares-new-single-im-a-man-listen-watch-video-3588010">《I&#39;m A Man》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kim-gordon-announces-solo-lp-the-collective-and-shares-lead-single-bye-bye-3571769">《BYE BYE》</a>等单曲。这是戈登 2019 年首张个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kim-gordon-no-home-record-album-review-2555109">《No Home Record》之后的作品。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-kim-gordons-disorientating-new-single-ecrp-3768610">查看 Kim Gordon 令人迷失方向的新单曲“ECRP”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
